== 建筑 ==
* 1950年：Bennett House, 3901 Riverview Blvd. in [[布雷登顿|Bradenton]], Florida
* 1956年：David Cohen House, Siesta Key, Sarasota, Florida<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://archrecord.construction.com/projects/residential/archives/PDFs/rudolf.pdf |title=''Open plan, prefab units cut Florida costs'' in ''Record Houses 1956'' |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2004-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040213110021/http://archrecord.construction.com/projects/residential/archives/PDFs/rudolf.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
